    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">A lightning rod has been placed in a city at the position <var>P</var>. This lightning rod will absorb a thunderbolt that strikes a nearby area with a distance of up to <var>D</var>.<br><br>More specifically, the lightning rod will absorb thunderbolts that strike a position between <var>P</var> - <var>D</var> and <var>P</var> + <var>D</var>.<br><br>Now, a thunderstorm will occur, and <var>N</var> thunderbolts will strike. Output the number of thunderbolts that the lightning rod will absorb.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> Three space separated integers <var>N</var>, <var>P</var>, and <var>D</var>.<br><strong>Next <var>N</var> lines:</strong> An integer <var>x</var> that specifies where a thunderbolt will strike.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\">A single line containing how many thunderbolts will be absorbed by the lightning rod.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; <var>N</var>,<var>D</var> &le; 100<br>-100 &le; <var>P</var>,<var>x</var> &le; 100</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">1 0 3\n0</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">1</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
